Name: Xeno Shooter
About the game: Xeno Shooter is a action shooter arena game! You play as a space cadet who travels to Andromeda with the mission of defeating the Primordials and thus, achieving a new home for humanity. The game have internal achievments. This is a short game with challenging arenas, some platform stages and some bosses in an retro pixelart. We hope you enjoy your adventure in Andromeda and manage to defeat all 4 Primordials! Good Luck! :) Musics by: Igor Abdu Aguiar and Victor Luccas Frey
Developers: Crazy Dino Game Studio,Felipe Mauricio,Octavio Gomes,Victor Luccas Frey
